<h2>2. Check program-specific requirements</h2>
</div></div>


<div class="wysiwyg parbase section">
<div class="rte">
<p><span class="xlarge-text">Some programs require you to provide <b>additional documents specific to the department to which you are applying</b>. It is your responsibility to <a adhocenable="false" href="http://www.concordia.ca/admissions/undergraduate/programs-with-additional-requirements.html">verify if your program has additional requirements</a> (e.g., letters of intent, portfolios, interviews, auditions and specific deadlines).</span></p>

